{"id": "1198329617166114827", "channel_id": "1198329617166114827", "type": 0, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "首先，先夸夸忘却前夜写丽兹故事的文案。\n\n这是我个人目前最喜欢的剧情，短短4个小故事加上1个命轮故事。\n\n个人觉得，它对丽兹角色的塑造以及这5个小故事中对于生命价值的展现，已经远远超出了一个普通游戏人物故事的深度。\n\n可能包含我个人的过度解读，但我真的真的很喜欢这个故事。\n\n也不知道，文案在创作的时候有没有参考伍尔芙的《飞蛾之死》，反正，请先收下我的膝盖。\n\n比起环娜，老套路的穿越剧情。\n丽兹的剧情真正打动了我，个人的解读以及伍尔芙《飞蛾之死》原文如下\n，文笔不好，还请守密人们见谅。\n\n也期待忘却前夜的文案能写出更多丽兹这样的剧情。", "timestamp": "2024-01-20T18:14:04.620000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-20T18:14:25.508000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1198329617602334883", "filename": "Screenshot_20240120-184612_WPS_Office.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 200194, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1198329617166114827/1198329617602334883/Screenshot_20240120-184612_WPS_Office.jpg?ex=6a00caec&is=69ff796c&hm=7e6b607d4870f91e0e90b77ea5d73c7b8dfd7942616487374a8969fd41cb545b&"}, {"id": "1198329617921093773", "filename": "Screenshot_20240120-184616_WPS_Office.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 193406, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1198329617166114827/1198329617921093773/Screenshot_20240120-184616_WPS_Office.jpg?ex=6a00caec&is=69ff796c&hm=eaa7c1f4951e394006d3646657b72f8a76b4a7bf03fa48585ef83b93f08ae541&"}, {"id": "1198329618277617664", "filename": "Screenshot_20240120-184624_WPS_Office.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 188603, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1198329617166114827/1198329618277617664/Screenshot_20240120-184624_WPS_Office.jpg?ex=6a00caec&is=69ff796c&hm=2320fd7574567bfa1ae4fc4ea0dfa559b281a38dbceb1cb488af97388295608d&"}, {"id": "1198329618583793824", "filename": "Screenshot_20240120-184628_WPS_Office.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 182108, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1198329617166114827/1